<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Maintenance — MOCHISKIN</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Abel&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --peach-light : #FFE5D9;
            --peach-main  : #FFCDB2;
            --peach-dark  : #FFB4A2;
            --pink-light  : #FFD7E4;
            --pink-main   : #FFC2D1;
            --rose-light  : #FFF0F5;
            --gray-soft   : #6B6B6B;
            --white       : #FFFFFF;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Abel', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--gray-soft);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose-light) 0%, var(--peach-light) 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .maintenance-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem 4rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 180, 162, 0.25);
            max-width: 520px;
            width: 90%;
        }

        .maintenance-card .logo {
            font-family: 'Abel', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--peach-dark);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .maintenance-card h1 {
            font-family: 'Abel', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: var(--gray-soft);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .maintenance-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--gray-soft);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .maintenance-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--peach-main), var(--pink-main));
            color: var(--white);
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 60px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--peach-dark), var(--pink-main));
            border-radius: 2px;
            margin: 1rem auto 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="maintenance-card">
        <div class="logo">MOCHISKIN</div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <h1>Site en maintenance</h1>
        <p>Nous effectuons une mise à jour pour améliorer votre expérience.<br>
           Merci de votre patience, nous serons de retour très bientôt !</p>
        <span class="maintenance-badge">Bientôt de retour ✨</span>
    </div>
</body>
</html>